<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.2">
<l>meynna lattavat taittivat taittarum meyyaip poyyiṉaik kaiyilōr caṅkuṭai</l>
<l>mainni ṟakkaṭa laikkaṭal vaṇṇaṉai mālai yālilaip paḷḷikoḷ māyaṉai</l>
<l>neṉṉa laippaka laiyiṟṟai  nāḷiṉai nāḷai yāyvarum tiṅkaḷai yāṇṭiṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṉa laikkarum piṉiṭait tēṟalaik kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai [the one who is] penance</l>
<l rend="indent">which is good for the soul,</l>
<l>Truth which brings clarity, illusion, [he who is] the ink-colored sea</l>
<l rend="indent">with a conch in one hand,</l>
<l>The sea-hued one, Māl, Māyōṉ sleeping on the banyan leaf,</l>
<l rend="indent">yesterday, midday, this day,</l>
<l>A month which comes as tomorrows, a year, sugar candy</l>
<l rend="indent">and the juice within sugarcane.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
